                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17790113-10-off54 t17790113-10-crimeloc57"></join>, a person informed me my pocket was picked of my handkerchief; I saw the prisoner running. He was stopped, and the handkerchief was found upon him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17790113-10-person133">
                  MARTHA
                   LOAD
               <interp inst="t17790113-10-person133" type="surname" value="LOAD"></interp>
